{"tid":1770250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【警世】行動post推唔郁係有原因","createTime":"2019-12-05T08:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-06T02:50:41.000Z","uid":208412,"like":62,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"522e7f3c8c7026d8b3b2da016002fbc7d5159691","tid":1770250,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T08:53:38.000Z","msg":"有幾個原因相信大家都知<br />\n五毛推垃圾post<br />\n無善用不推文回覆<br />\n但主因應該係 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">行動Post無內容</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我想講 唔係貼幾張相 加幾句<br />\n「你哋係味唔記得咗義士烈士」<br />\n「屌你哋咁撚樣對唔對得住手足」<br />\n咁就叫行動post <br />\n<br />\n行動post推唔郁其中一個原因係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">冇內容</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">求生路線 <br />\n鄰近交通 <br />\n惡犬過去咬人地點<br />\n帶咩物資<br />\n注意事項</span></span><br />\n如果一個行動post 齊晒呢啲 <br />\n相信啲巴絲見到都特別用心推<br />\n<br />\n好多時唔少行動post都係咁<br />\n得一兩張相 加一兩句「對唔對得住手足」<br />\n跟住就會叫人喪推 <br />\n<br />\n呢啲所謂行動post實際資訊得張圖<br />\n我自己10秒睇晒 推 就已經可以出翻去<br />\n問心果句 我去遊行集會都想知邊到安全<br />\n有咩物資要預備啦<br />\n<br />\n如果有人屌我話<br />\n「去咗咁耐你應該知啦！」<br />\n但事實就係咁<br />\n好多人去咗港島好多次都未熟個地理位置<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: gold;\">幾十個呢啲post都唔及一個高汁行動post有用<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n以下係高質行動post例子<br />\n「長期置頂」727元朗反鄉黑遊行終極攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356464</a><br />\n<br />\n當然 我承認依家多咗唔少垃圾post上咗熱門<br />\n但69到而家已經半年 要醒嘅人一早醒咗<br />\n佢哋一早有渠道去接收資訊<br />\n<br />\n如果你話要令更加多人醒覺 <br />\n咁應該離開連登孤島去宣傳<br />\n就算你連登幾多正評 幾多人推都好<br />\nFB Twitter 連儂牆冇宣傳 <br />\n冇同外界宣傳都係無用"},{"pid":"facb3721b16e93b52ff3dfe3f8b00b23345c3d70","tid":1770250,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T08:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Cc0FhD.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Cc0FhD.gif&h=c151aa5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8a08f1a3372dbf0a4026aa9001cdf0348518f80","tid":1770250,"uid":76960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"班on9連咩叫&quot;行動&quot;都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話人唔推行動post, 跟本就冇行動post<br />\n個個post入到gi就得張文宣圖，屌你老母果啲叫宣傳post呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!"},{"pid":"e0e8145af25871b820857940aa1338bf5c54cd21","tid":1770250,"uid":208412,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a8a08f1a3372dbf0a4026aa9001cdf0348518f80","tid":1770250,"uid":76960,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T08:57:54.000Z","msg":"班on9連咩叫&quot;行動&quot;都未知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日話人唔推行動post, 跟本就冇行動post<br />\n個個post入到gi就得張文宣圖，屌你老母果啲叫宣傳post呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T08:59:22.000Z","msg":"依家出面又成堆128post 入到去全部一式一樣 長時間落去啲真正高質post只會沉晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e608f591308f7594330c41b1ce654b3633f4ab7b","tid":1770250,"uid":144000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"樓主小心 一陣啲人又屈你五毛㗎喇"},{"pid":"09d4c3f57d4500a578dd2d5ab763d5da81aaf58b","tid":1770250,"uid":83650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:01:22.000Z","msg":"12.8 維園見"},{"pid":"67fd472bf58bb38b3c6011bb98ed4646065af31d","tid":1770250,"uid":208412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e608f591308f7594330c41b1ce654b3633f4ab7b","tid":1770250,"uid":144000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:00:36.000Z","msg":"樓主小心 一陣啲人又屈你五毛㗎喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:01:49.000Z","msg":"咁都屈得落 連登就真係淪陷喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f477666f363e01eb2337fcde4c3bb8f6ea0e3ec","tid":1770250,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T09:05:39.000Z","msg":"同埋當成班人一齊推嘅話<br />\n個post